</node>
<node id="Annual Report on Form 10-K">
  <data key="d0">Annual Report on Form 10-K</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The Annual Report on Form 10-K is a mandatory document that provides a comprehensive overview of a company's financial performance and overall financial condition, filed annually with the Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC). This report is essential for investors and regulators as it includes detailed financial statements and related notes, management’s discussion and analysis, and other significant information about the company’s operations, performance, and risks.

The document is utilized by various companies, such as NVIDIA, KLAC, Broadcom, and Arista, to disclose their financial statements, which include income statements, balance sheets, and cash flow statements. In addition to the core financial data, the report contains forward-looking statements, cautionary notes, and management assessments which aim to provide insights into the company’s future outlook and performance.

Each filing of the Annual Report on Form 10-K offers important updates on accounting policies and tax matters, ensuring full transparency regarding the company’s financial status. This annual document serves as a crucial tool for stakeholders to evaluate the fiscal health and operational efficacy of the companies involved.&lt;SEP&gt;The Annual Report on Form 10-K is a comprehensive report submitted annually by ANET to the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission, detailing the company's financial performance and risks.&lt;SEP&gt;The Annual Report on Form 10-K is an annual disclosure document that the company is required to file with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission, detailing its financial performance and other significant information.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f0b30e55c2d2c942c8ef27807467b3d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91ba0c40d4695fe5428e9f1aaee99693&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4612ab0f41075ef25aa4070b5715ec41&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19032b9d0addd28842932a48ea8fd697&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cb82fb0b57380bdf7abd3bbcae084048&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-88fbdee009d132142f267759b80b8fcd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2bcf7035b2263b22ce2270c9abedd363&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-860e208223be2b88258c7bc409f5f9bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c2950a5595514c07bb3ab4a5efe970d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6646d6be107845318b9e01fd74b6a79</data>
