  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The headquarters location of NVIDIA in California.&lt;SEP&gt;Santa Clara is the city in California where Applied Materials, Inc. reported its financial results from.&lt;SEP&gt;Santa Clara is a city in California, serving as the headquarters for Intel Corporation.&lt;SEP&gt;Santa Clara is the location in California where land and improvements were purchased for a property project.&lt;SEP&gt;Santa Clara is a city in California where a new building is being constructed related to the operation and expansion of a business.&lt;SEP&gt;Santa Clara is the city in California where Arista Networks, Inc. is headquartered.</data>
