  <data key="d2">Data Center revenue for fiscal year 2026 increased by 68%, driven by platform shifts in computing and AI.&lt;SEP&gt;Data Center is a facility used to house computer systems and associated components, part of Arista Networks' client-to-cloud networking solutions.</data>
