  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Inventories are tracked to manage cost of sales for inventory provisions and to write-down obsolete or excess inventory.&lt;SEP&gt;Inventories is a financial data point representing the total value of all goods held by a company for future sale.</data>
