<node id="Form 10-K">
  <data key="d0">Form 10-K</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Form 10-K is an annual report filed by publicly traded companies with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) that provides a comprehensive summary of a company's financial performance and significant accounting policies for a specific fiscal year. This document is crucial as it includes detailed financial statements, such as Consolidated Financial Statements, and critical notes that clarify these statements, including any significant changes like goodwill impairment. 

Companies are mandated to submit Form 10-K annually, ensuring transparency and providing essential insights into their financial health. It encompasses vital information regarding a company's outstanding shares, financial results, and overall operational status. Prominent corporations, including AMD and Broadcom Inc., are required to file this report, which plays a significant role in fulfilling legal obligations and fostering investor confidence in the financial markets. 

The Form 10-K serves not only as a detailed financial report but also as a mechanism for annual disclosure, encompassing financial data related to various components such as income taxes, which are specifically highlighted in detailed notes within the report. By consolidating the company's financial information, Form 10-K acts as a primary source for stakeholders to assess the company's performance and operational viability.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fe1fafd9b0c6f09af84ad373757a9b00&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a36df99dfa3a16bd8e4d429df7cf42a6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-26fa1d1070f941c3c83605779a2af8f0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-737963f5a4aa4c7ac5ff75bd66cabe60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1329332311e82d0b2cc6f7232bfaa092&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d780eacfb91e291d22055bf3aca31fa3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e3082390d4ae9b34c69f94e2ec0135c5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5128d467897e9a6a1ea6d801c0966d6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7df88c2c7b38c5eb12580560b4e0dc2d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9c17cee8b5d4c0058ad449ca8d769b9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42aa9c7f7d4ca12621cf2af559e1aa29&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69f1af12f4eafcde14c51426aec9aa50&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9c9d9262cc591e5a663ff1343e1ab5b9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ca05e43c085b4801092259d8bb642b30</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
