<node id="Purchase Obligations">
  <data key="d0">Purchase Obligations</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Purchase obligations are commitments to buy certain products or services in the future, which, when associated with H20 excess inventory, led to a significant charge.&lt;SEP&gt;Purchase Obligations amount to $10.6 billion for goods and services as of October 26, 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;Non-cancelable purchase commitments for cloud computing web services, data centers, software, license, and services.</data>
