<node id="SEC">
  <data key="d0">SEC</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) is the principal regulatory body in the United States responsible for overseeing securities trading and enforcing securities laws. The SEC plays a crucial role in ensuring transparency and accuracy in the financial reporting of publicly traded companies. It mandates that these companies, including Broadcom, file periodic reports such as the Annual Report on Form 10-K to maintain compliance with regulations.

In the context of corporate reporting, the SEC is where companies, including Broadcom, submit their financial statements and disclosures. ARM, for example, also must prepare and distribute periodic reports in accordance with the SEC’s guidelines. The Commission’s regulations are designed to protect investors by promoting fair and efficient markets, and it has the authority to impose penalties for violations of securities laws, thereby maintaining corporate accountability.

Overall, the SEC is essential for maintaining the integrity of the financial markets in the U.S., guiding companies on their reporting obligations, and ensuring that investors have access to vital financial information.&lt;SEP&gt;The SEC (Securities and Exchange Commission) regulates securities trading in the U.S. and may impose penalties for violations.&lt;SEP&gt;The SEC, or Securities and Exchange Commission, is the U.S. regulatory body overseeing securities laws and companies' disclosures.&lt;SEP&gt;The SEC, or Securities and Exchange Commission, is the U.S. government agency that oversees securities transactions, activities of financial professionals, and the stock market.&lt;SEP&gt;The SEC (Securities and Exchange Commission) is a U.S. government agency that regulates the securities industry and protects investors.&lt;SEP&gt;The SEC (Securities and Exchange Commission) is a U.S. government agency responsible for enforcing securities laws and regulating the securities industry.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3f2ce3a4f3492cdc62d91339c8332500&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a05220306950555c6367d2f0c69cb622&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5128d467897e9a6a1ea6d801c0966d6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09305c77610bfec18789bdfc44505242&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7268957cde14a4d3b9ad39486be2220a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b9cf777435ca6135f2543fc921d450ba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-369a5552d7a3758ad27f4b784ffe7595&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-227b552d2bdbe48a2b38c898a9b49229&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8324363f0a048e57166b3353e15ed038</data>
