<node id="United States">
  <data key="d0">United States</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The United States is a prominent economic and political entity known for its considerable influence on global trade and business practices. As of fiscal year 2026, the United States accounts for 31% of NVIDIA's total revenue and contributed 11% to the net revenue of a major company in 2025. This country serves as a critical base for numerous companies, including AMAT, which conduct extensive product development and manufacturing activities within its borders.

Engaging in global trade, the United States has implemented various trade policies and export regulations that significantly impact the business landscape. Its trade practices, including tariffs, affect a multitude of customers and suppliers located both domestically and internationally. Furthermore, the United States is contemplating the adoption of laws and regulations regarding artificial intelligence (AI), which could directly influence AI's application in product development.

In addition to its economic policies, the United States maintains a jurisdiction where companies must adhere to income tax laws that substantially affect their tax liabilities. Businesses operating in the country also face a comprehensive array of laws and regulations encompassing financial disclosures, securities, and corporate governance, underscoring the United States' pivotal role in global business operations.

Moreover, the United States is striving for greater end-to-end control over its semiconductor architecture, which contributes to fragmentation in the global semiconductor market. This pursuit reflects broader concerns within the industry about maintaining competitiveness and security in technology.

The management of personal data within the United States is governed by various laws and regulations, particularly concerning the import of such data from other regions. This regulatory framework is crucial for companies like ANET that operate in this environment and must contend with tariffs and other economic policies impacting their operations.

Additionally, the United States is currently engaged in bilateral trade negotiations with China focusing on export controls and regulations, further highlighting its active role in shaping international economic relations. Lastly, it is significant to note that the Inflation Reduction Act of 2022 was signed into law in the United States, representing a key legislative effort impacting various sectors of the economy.&lt;SEP&gt;The United States is the country where the Bureau of Industry and Security operates and where relevant export regulations are implemented.&lt;SEP&gt;The United States is a geographical location representing a significant market for revenue, contributing to overall financial performance.&lt;SEP&gt;The United States is the country in which the One Big Beautiful Bill Act was enacted.&lt;SEP&gt;The United States is mentioned as a jurisdiction where the subject is subject to income taxes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dd5f5a1a7c540b1c8cafe05b35cfd7fb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f50e3434e5c216500628bf58a9da4be1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-26fa1d1070f941c3c83605779a2af8f0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7200d8553fd2e4a1586cd2f8af4129fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-99b76900a97d7c959bc5ca885c3601da&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-625ca1cf50e3b24380c8601c96bdd7a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85c73190292489fe36964fdd5fc32b0c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5d99a02cc7061af948a4068d7dfaf580&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1b0f36135b3b08cac0302bf342d7918d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d8ee469fd420dd945b64b580faff532&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-940cea73a3ab3826472368a5d0f388bc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e356de4d5460f722f331512046c5047&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5776951d5c25cce5d7ce7eb72c02bd77&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a607ffbfac50d0f1129f1e67cb61a773&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c2950a5595514c07bb3ab4a5efe970d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b85ec976f34913889413e19b8bcf3a78&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed2b32ad29a09feed46df0c963169feb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-71dff42efadaa177f60791628d62844c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c5e7cc3c7c57e107c4d688872735f76a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3fdce1044a2c44a0e983bbcf60375f53</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1777382509</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
