  <data key="d2">The Five-Year Credit Agreement is a financial agreement allowing the company to borrow up to $2.0 billion, expiring in February 2030.&lt;SEP&gt;The Five-Year Credit Agreement is a financial agreement worth $2.0 billion, set to expire in February 2030 unless extended. It includes financial covenants and was in compliance as of October 26, 2025, with no amounts outstanding on that date.</data>
