<node id="Tax Cuts and Jobs Act">
  <data key="d0">Tax Cuts and Jobs Act</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The Tax Cuts and Jobs Act, enacted on December 22, 2017, requires a one-time transition tax on certain unrepatriated earnings of foreign subsidiaries, with one remaining payment of $255 million due in February 2026.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-217dcca296bd42c2a1d26c339d20ff32</data>
