  <data key="d0">Corporate Alternative Minimum Tax Credits</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Corporate Alternative Minimum Tax (CAMT) credits are tax credits that are not expected to be realized due to changes in the timing of future tax deductions following the enactment of the One Big Beautiful Bill Act.</data>
