  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Asia">
  <data key="d0">Asia</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Asia is one of the primary locations where AMAT conducts its product development and manufacturing activities.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;Asia is a region where the organization conducts certain manufacturing, supply chain, and other operations to be closer to customers and reduce costs.&lt;SEP&gt;Asia is a significant location for generating revenues, hosting a substantial portion of the world’s semiconductor manufacturing capacity.&lt;SEP&gt;Asia is a significant region for the company's revenues, hosting a substantial portion of the world’s semiconductor manufacturing capacity.&lt;SEP&gt;Asia is the geographic region where a limited number of third-party foundries offering leading-edge manufacturing processes are concentrated.&lt;SEP&gt;Asia is a geographic region from which price-focused competition, especially from China, is experienced by the company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-26fa1d1070f941c3c83605779a2af8f0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7200d8553fd2e4a1586cd2f8af4129fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4cef59817c38511355f56938f73f6db2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1329332311e82d0b2cc6f7232bfaa092&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-01c84b34cab452ecda64e168d9c9ea38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c84b525ec6385a6df80b84b52431bb29</data>
