<node id="Operating Activities">
  <data key="d0">Operating Activities</data>
  <data key="d1">activity</data>
  <data key="d2">Operating Activities refers to the cash flow from the core business operations of the company, including income and expenses.&lt;SEP&gt;Operating Activities involve cash flows generated from a company's core business operations, including adjustments for non-cash items.&lt;SEP&gt;Operating Activities involve cash flows generated from a company's core business operations, including adjustments for non-cash items.&lt;SEP&gt;Operating activities include the primary revenue-generating activities of a company.&lt;SEP&gt;Operating Activities include net income, adjusted for non-cash items, and changes in operating assets and liabilities.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b976a275590777e7877d2d66b5f6379c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20ff684928510a0aa4726b57cf95bfc6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b38febc44090948b4632a44869ab7045&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-88fbdee009d132142f267759b80b8fcd</data>
