<node id="Financing Activities">
  <data key="d0">Financing Activities</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Financing Activities encompasses cash flows related to financing the company, including stock repurchases, dividends, and debt repayments.&lt;SEP&gt;Financing activities pertain to cash flows from financing the business, including debt repayments and stock repurchases, for the fiscal year ended June 30, 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;Financing Activities refers to the cash flows from repayment of debt, stock repurchases, and payment of dividends.&lt;SEP&gt;Financing Activities consist of cash flows related to borrowing, repayment, and equity transactions such as dividends and stock repurchases.&lt;SEP&gt;Financing Activities consist of cash flows related to borrowing, repayment, and equity transactions such as dividends and stock repurchases.&lt;SEP&gt;Financing Activities involve cash flows related to the company's financing strategies, such as debt or equity financing.&lt;SEP&gt;Financing activities involve cash transactions related to borrowing and repaying debt, issuing stock, and repurchasing shares.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b976a275590777e7877d2d66b5f6379c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bfac3dde6482c2f8fd9ea0e0c659c15b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fcbd467e0d3d2d1e90e50929e4ef4372&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20ff684928510a0aa4726b57cf95bfc6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-88fbdee009d132142f267759b80b8fcd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42aa9c7f7d4ca12621cf2af559e1aa29&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ff8c5ead4252ae2a31532cc82caa936</data>
