<node id="Capital Expenditures">
  <data key="d0">Capital Expenditures</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Capital Expenditures (CapEx) are defined as funds employed by a company to acquire, upgrade, or maintain physical assets, which may include property, industrial buildings, or equipment. This category is significant in the cash flows from investing activities, illustrating the financial investments necessary for the operational efficiency of a firm. 

In financial terms, Capital Expenditures reported expenses amounting to -$646 million in 2026 and -$381 million in 2025, reflecting a decrease of $7.9 million that directly impacts cash flows from investing activities. This decline indicates a cautious approach to investment or potential changes in operational strategies over these fiscal periods.

Furthermore, projections suggest that Capital Expenditures are anticipated to rise in fiscal year 2026, which implies an expected increase in investments that may cater to the acquisition or enhancement of physical assets. Specifically, within the semiconductor industry, Capital Expenditures also encompass the essential financial outlays needed for manufacturing and assembly facilities, as well as technology development.

Overall, Capital Expenditures serve as a critical element of a company's budgeting and financial planning, playing a vital role in the growth and maintenance of its physical asset base.&lt;SEP&gt;Capital Expenditures are costs incurred by a company to acquire, upgrade, or maintain physical assets such as buildings or equipment, mentioned in the context of business operation and expansion.&lt;SEP&gt;Capital expenditures are funds used by companies to acquire, upgrade, or maintain physical assets such as property, industrial buildings, or equipment.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b976a275590777e7877d2d66b5f6379c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-43a8f055527dad4e87136bbd01caf743&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b33403642cf163673735a8236b77616c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6914852673b586e472efa313d90a7cbf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fcbd467e0d3d2d1e90e50929e4ef4372&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e0837ab88a60a72e576353a5fe0398b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f6b26aa2f7f768941f9a0f229275f9c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42aa9c7f7d4ca12621cf2af559e1aa29&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6646d6be107845318b9e01fd74b6a79&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-059f0081c4b3b76f83407aeceac32785</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
