<node id="Management">
  <data key="d0">Management</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Management is the team or group of individuals responsible for overseeing the operations and strategic direction of a company. This includes both daily management and long-term strategic planning, which requires evaluating the company's performance through various financial measures, including both GAAP and non-GAAP standards. This dual focus allows management to provide comprehensive insights into the company's financial health, making adjustments as necessary to ensure accurate representation for stakeholders.

Furthermore, management has a critical role in assessing and managing material risks, particularly from cybersecurity threats. This entails implementing effective risk mitigation plans and processes to protect the organization from potential security breaches. Additionally, changes in management personnel can significantly influence company performance and market perception, highlighting the importance of stable leadership in navigating potential diversions, such as those arising from acquisitions.

Overall, management encompasses the key personnel who make crucial strategic decisions and facilitate operational oversight, ensuring that both immediate operational objectives and long-term strategic goals align with the company’s performance and risk management needs.&lt;SEP&gt;Management refers to the team or department within the company responsible for making decisions regarding financial reporting, including tax provisions.&lt;SEP&gt;Management is responsible for formulating restructuring plans based on estimates and available information.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d30ee8565f60986af2412d44782de3b8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-28d0d279e198946ca35e2e93f3701350&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d780eacfb91e291d22055bf3aca31fa3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db288d888bd9fbe8abf743c9d16d17a9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9d385d153b391ba0f835b4e1b0862be&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-063cbc70b0b679d3caa2cb95ecd87963&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2bcf7035b2263b22ce2270c9abedd363&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3fdce1044a2c44a0e983bbcf60375f53</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1777382510</data>
