<node id="Joint Ventures">
  <data key="d0">Joint Ventures</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Joint Ventures are companies formed in collaboration between two or more parties, which may decline in value or fail to meet objectives.&lt;SEP&gt;Joint ventures are business collaborations that can impact AMD's operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Joint ventures are cooperative arrangements between two or more parties to undertake economic activity, sharing risks, rewards, and management responsibilities.&lt;SEP&gt;Joint ventures are cooperative arrangements between two or more parties to undertake economic activity, sharing risks, rewards, and management responsibilities.</data>
