<node id="Cybersecurity">
  <data key="d0">Cybersecurity</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Cybersecurity pertains to the protection of an acquired company's digital assets and the prevention of cyber threats, which is essential for safeguarding sensitive information.&lt;SEP&gt;Cybersecurity refers to the protection of information systems from theft or damage, which could be threatened by new technologies.&lt;SEP&gt;Cybersecurity refers to the protection of information systems from theft or damage, which could be threatened by new technologies.&lt;SEP&gt;Cybersecurity concerns involve protecting computer systems and networks from damage, theft, or unauthorized access, affecting trade measures.&lt;SEP&gt;Cybersecurity is the practice of protecting systems, networks, and data from digital attacks, a relevant consideration in the networking market.&lt;SEP&gt;Cybersecurity refers to the measures the Company must take to protect its digital assets and comply with related laws and regulations in its international operations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-99b76900a97d7c959bc5ca885c3601da&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b09f9d54d4cb00356f5ae233ac0e55c8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2674cda5d2c8571334c7ce0cb7e9fb3f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-61f3bc12aec2296a1fa9ad0ee19d3d6d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-88f2b4d088361dd806e394a19506ee8f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6757e425a6551576cf75d5c43bed978b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-059f0081c4b3b76f83407aeceac32785</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1777382059</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Privacy Policies">
  <data key="d0">Privacy Policies</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Privacy Policies are the guidelines and rules that govern how an acquired company manages, protects, and processes personal data, ensuring compliance with data protection laws.&lt;SEP&gt;Privacy policies are statements made by businesses regarding their collection, use, and protection of personal information.&lt;SEP&gt;Privacy policies are statements made by businesses regarding their collection, use, and protection of personal information.</data>
