  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Anti-Corruption pertains to the policies and measures that an acquired company adopts to prevent bribery, corruption, and unethical business practices.&lt;SEP&gt;Anti-Corruption laws and regulations that the Company must comply with in its international operations.</data>
