<node id="Patent Applications">
  <data key="d0">Patent Applications</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Patent Applications are formal requests made to a patent office for granting a patent for an invention, which can be affected by changes in intellectual property laws and their interpretation.&lt;SEP&gt;Pending patent applications that the company has filed, seeking protection for some of its products and technologies.&lt;SEP&gt;Patent Applications are requests filed with a patent office to obtain a patent for an invention, outlining its details and claims.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-158df076948257685462bdd5a2ffcd95&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c3b4f2c79e964eb1c327adb0e6e96fea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2fd81b548154c0653391bff9d78b2285</data>
