<node id="Cybersecurity Threats">
  <data key="d0">Cybersecurity Threats</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Cybersecurity Threats are potential vulnerabilities, attacks, or breaches that target information technology systems with the aim of stealing, corrupting, or otherwise compromising data and information.&lt;SEP&gt;Cybersecurity Threats are risks that threaten the confidentiality, integrity, and availability of KLA's IT Systems and Confidential Information, originating from diverse threat actors and attack vectors.&lt;SEP&gt;Cybersecurity threats represent risks to IT systems from unauthorized access and attacks that could adversely affect business integrity.&lt;SEP&gt;Cybersecurity Threats refer to various risks involving unauthorized access or attacks on IT systems, potentially harming business operations and reputation.&lt;SEP&gt;Cybersecurity threats represent risks to IT systems from unauthorized access and attacks that could adversely affect business integrity.&lt;SEP&gt;Cybersecurity Threats refer to various risks involving unauthorized access or attacks on IT systems, potentially harming business operations and reputation.&lt;SEP&gt;Cybersecurity threats refer to risks that affect the security of systems and data, which are increasing in complexity and number.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-158df076948257685462bdd5a2ffcd95&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e74b16856b8a1a3ddf8e77f75d7175ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a592bb47c530d6e0ab16b656b695aa6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b09f9d54d4cb00356f5ae233ac0e55c8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-06830ee957dabca2d7296c8cec7e538f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1777381668</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Information Technology Systems">
  <data key="d0">Information Technology Systems</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Information Technology Systems are the computer and telecommunications systems used to collect, use, transmit, store, and process data, which are subject to disruptions, outages, failures, and security breaches or incidents.&lt;SEP&gt;Information technology systems encompass hardware, software, and networks used to process and manage data and information.&lt;SEP&gt;Information technology systems encompass hardware, software, and networks used to process and manage data and information.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-158df076948257685462bdd5a2ffcd95&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-61f3bc12aec2296a1fa9ad0ee19d3d6d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
