  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Confidential Information">
  <data key="d0">Confidential Information</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Confidential Information is sensitive data that is not publicly available and belongs to the company, its customers, or other business partners, which needs to be protected from unauthorized access or misuse.&lt;SEP&gt;Confidential Information includes confidential data, transactional data, IP, and personal information of individuals associated with KLA, its customers, and business partners.&lt;SEP&gt;Confidential Information refers to sensitive data that requires protection and restoration efforts, and is critical for business operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Confidential information includes sensitive data that must be protected from unauthorized access and disclosures.&lt;SEP&gt;Confidential information includes sensitive data that must be protected from unauthorized access and disclosures.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-158df076948257685462bdd5a2ffcd95&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-adf3cdd028d63a6900c51e0d73fc800e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e74b16856b8a1a3ddf8e77f75d7175ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b09f9d54d4cb00356f5ae233ac0e55c8</data>
