<node id="Personal Information">
  <data key="d0">Personal Information</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Personal Information is data that can be used to identify an individual, which is collected and processed by the company and is subject to protection under privacy and data protection laws.&lt;SEP&gt;Personal information includes confidential and proprietary data collected and processed by the organization in its business operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Personal information refers to data that can identify an individual and is subject to various privacy laws and protections.&lt;SEP&gt;Personal information includes confidential and proprietary data collected and processed by the organization in its business operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Personal information refers to data that can identify an individual and is subject to various privacy laws and protections.</data>
