<node id="Third-Party Providers">
  <data key="d0">Third-Party Providers</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Third-party providers supply AI capabilities, and reliance on them is crucial for the successful implementation of AI in business operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Third-Party Providers are external organizations that own and maintain systems used by the company for data processing, which may be involved in cybersecurity incidents.&lt;SEP&gt;Third-Party Providers are external organizations that provide services and products, including IT systems, to KLA and are involved in the collection, use, transmission, and storage of Confidential Information.</data>
