  <data key="d0">Business Combinations</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Business Combinations refer to the process of merging or consolidating businesses, which involves numerous risks to the company's financial condition and operations.&lt;SEP&gt;The process of accounting for business acquisitions, which requires significant estimates and assumptions.&lt;SEP&gt;The process of accounting for business acquisitions, which requires significant estimates and assumptions.</data>
