<node id="Company">
  <data key="d0">Company</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Company is a multifaceted organization engaged in various operations, including acquisitions, legal proceedings, and the implementation of sustainability strategies. It has indicated that Pillar Two did not materially affect its financial statements or operations for the fiscal year ending March 31, 2025. The Company is heavily involved in product development and licensing, particularly within the high-value segment, and its activities are influenced by broader economic conditions and trade policies.

Financially, the Company participates in share-based compensation, goodwill assessments, and income tax accounting. It faces significant fluctuations in its results from one period to another, caused by various factors such as agreements, financial terms, and market conditions. The Company also generates a portion of its revenue from sales to government entities and channel partners, while grappling with the associated risks and challenges of these sales channels. Additionally, the Company emphasizes the importance of designing products using open-source software and entering into licensing agreements, which are central to its operational and financial framework.

In terms of governance, the Company is required to obtain shareholder approval for issuing securities and must oversee related party transactions. It also conducts meetings for independent directors and has outlined specific terms regarding ordinary shares and procedures for managing shareholder complaints in its articles. Furthermore, the Company is dedicated to protecting its intellectual property rights and faces challenges associated with unauthorized access and legal claims, reflecting its commitment to governance and accountability in its multifarious undertakings.&lt;SEP&gt;The company in question is involved in financial reporting, Non-GAAP financial measures, and is subject to regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-625ca1cf50e3b24380c8601c96bdd7a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-13f18e1b9ab8662fc4105918eb9e67e8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e2d85f7a44ae4d46a5296c95183929c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-37906de44c22f23501372f2b90cd5aa7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b16721bd4c3f195f2ea0c219b1a93e14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25056dc4aba0a40a47c338bbf9630c33&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a0a44d9347461f9065271ab343488c5c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-789e78a4c56dfc29b3f11f7927499d10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-483298b8ddab3276baf8040d8034d01b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-caf1bb802539f8961349a60bf6c9b66c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e93e15b4141cb7def18652c3c8a45d8e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b7719f4025b95e35216526990a93506c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f17cd98c1d92584816e127c394e7ad1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6757e425a6551576cf75d5c43bed978b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c84b525ec6385a6df80b84b52431bb29&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daa7b8544edadd0f701ab9d8efd26b8e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-910ac36ac071842241018eea8ce214a8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5fd247a952683a47a5830843ce2924e4</data>
