<node id="Product Liability">
  <data key="d0">Product Liability</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Product liability refers to the legal responsibility for damages caused by defective products, which is a risk for the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Product liability involves legal claims against a company due to product defects or safety issues, which can affect financial conditions.&lt;SEP&gt;Product liability involves legal claims against a company due to product defects or safety issues, which can affect financial conditions.</data>
