  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Indemnification is a legal obligation where the company may be required to compensate customers for claims made against them by third parties.&lt;SEP&gt;Indemnification is a legal concept where one party compensates another for a loss, which is relevant in IP claims context.</data>
