<node id="Legal Proceedings">
  <data key="d0">Legal Proceedings</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Legal Proceedings are the formal processes of law, which may be initiated in case of violations of regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Legal proceedings are formal legal actions, claims, or lawsuits that the company may be involved in, related to various matters.&lt;SEP&gt;Legal Proceedings are formal legal actions that can arise from IP or confidential information disputes, impacting a company's operations and finances.&lt;SEP&gt;Legal Proceedings encompass the various processes related to lawsuits, claims, and litigation concerning IP rights among different parties.&lt;SEP&gt;Legal Proceedings encompass the various processes related to lawsuits, claims, and litigation concerning IP rights among different parties.&lt;SEP&gt;Legal proceedings encompass litigation and regulatory investigations that can impact a company's management and resources.</data>
