<node id="Restructuring Charges">
  <data key="d0">Restructuring Charges</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Restructuring Charges are costs associated with restructuring activities, amounting to $12 in 2026 and not applicable in 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;Restructuring Charges are costs associated with a workforce reduction plan announced by Applied Materials, Inc. in the fourth quarter of fiscal 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;Restructuring Charges amount to $7.7 million for the year ended June 30, 2025, related to the restructuring of the former PCB and Display operating segment.&lt;SEP&gt;Restructuring Charges are costs associated with changes in the organization and business processes, including employee terminations or exit costs.&lt;SEP&gt;Restructuring Charges are costs associated with restructuring activities, which were $76 million for Fiscal Year 2025.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;Restructuring Charges are costs associated with restructuring activities, which were $76 million for Fiscal Year 2025.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;Restructuring charges refer to costs related to organizational restructuring plans, primarily concerning employee severance and benefit arrangements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-43a8f055527dad4e87136bbd01caf743&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3a29194982b15aafff922b31789e91ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d8c3943d4fcccf1ae19651cf71f87bf4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-706c3addabed1cbc496a03d35fbb0b1b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7df88c2c7b38c5eb12580560b4e0dc2d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-34fac0adf4c8e15583c5a62a870fb1d5</data>
