  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Forward-Looking Statements are statements in the press release that include anticipations and expectations regarding the company's future performance and are subject to risks and uncertainties.&lt;SEP&gt;Forward-looking statements are statements in the press release that concern anticipated benefits and expectations of AMD's strategic partnership with Meta and involve risks and uncertainties.&lt;SEP&gt;Forward-looking statements are predictions concerning Broadcom's expected future business and financial performance, subject to risks and uncertainties.&lt;SEP&gt;Forward-looking statements are projections or expectations regarding future events or performance made by companies in their financial disclosures.</data>
