<node id="LAYER_A">
  <data key="d0">LAYER_A</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">LAYER_A is referenced as a specific layer or section within various financial or operational documents related to multiple entities, including AMD, Arm Holdings, and Broadcom Inc. In the context of AMD, LAYER_A contains financial information and data, serving as a category that pertains to the company’s financial reporting or data segmentation.

Additionally, LAYER_A is also associated with Arm Holdings, where it is featured in the operational context and earnings press releases. Here, LAYER_A may represent categories within Arm's operations or product lines, highlighting its relevance to Arm's financial disclosures.

Furthermore, LAYER_A is identified within Broadcom Inc.'s annual business report, where it similarly denotes a specific layer of information pertinent to financial reporting. Additionally, LAYER_A is mentioned in the context of annual risk reports, indicating its role in presenting key data related to risk management and assessment.

In summary, LAYER_A serves as a versatile element within various documentation frameworks, linking it to complex financial landscapes across different organizations.&lt;SEP&gt;LAYER_A refers to a specific layer or section within the context of Broadcom Inc.'s annual business report.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;LAYER_A refers to a specific layer or section within the annual risk report document.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bde81dfa7c0130867695a7023e89cf63&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0a83ce1ab52e2df80576ef179eeec72&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42b87cf93df46f504c0e370bbcbc6d94&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-54b2dd7afb5853f7b9fcb8fff6544b20&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a05220306950555c6367d2f0c69cb622&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d1f6742e80ed84d267cfe46fa7c9e31&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5128d467897e9a6a1ea6d801c0966d6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3de34ec76f3a0a44857b72c2f6e55416</data>
