<node id="Inflation Reduction Act of 2022">
  <data key="d0">Inflation Reduction Act of 2022</data>
  <data key="d1">legislation</data>
  <data key="d2">The Inflation Reduction Act of 2022 is legislation that enacted a 1% excise tax on stock repurchases, affecting AMD's financial planning.&lt;SEP&gt;The Inflation Reduction Act of 2022 is legislation that enacted a 1% excise tax on stock repurchases, affecting AMD's financial planning.&lt;SEP&gt;The Inflation Reduction Act of 2022 is legislation that enacted a 1% excise tax on stock repurchases, affecting AMD's financial planning.&lt;SEP&gt;The Inflation Reduction Act of 2022 is legislation that includes a 1% excise tax on stock repurchases, affecting AMD's financial planning.&lt;SEP&gt;The Inflation Reduction Act of 2022 includes provisions affecting stock repurchases, particularly regarding excise taxes.&lt;SEP&gt;The Inflation Reduction Act of 2022 includes provisions related to excise taxes imposed on stock repurchases.&lt;SEP&gt;The Inflation Reduction Act of 2022 includes provisions such as a 1% excise tax on certain stock repurchases by publicly traded companies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bde81dfa7c0130867695a7023e89cf63&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0a83ce1ab52e2df80576ef179eeec72&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42b87cf93df46f504c0e370bbcbc6d94&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-54b2dd7afb5853f7b9fcb8fff6544b20&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0292dbc49bc4382dc3bccb8e9b403c95&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e87a4f351685e936b673b5d8beb0687a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a607ffbfac50d0f1129f1e67cb61a773</data>
