<node id="PRC">
  <data key="d0">PRC</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The People's Republic of China (PRC) is a major country that plays a significant role in global trade and geopolitical affairs, heavily influencing international relations and economic policies. The PRC's government decisions, particularly in tandem with those of the United States, can greatly affect the business operations of various entities, including major players in the semiconductor and technology sectors such as Arm China and IPLA. This interconnectedness underscores the complex relationship between governmental actions and private business interests.

Within the PRC, which includes economically significant regions such as Hong Kong and Macau, the market is vital for companies like ARM, providing a substantial portion of their revenue. The dependency of international firms on the PRC's market accentuates its essentiality in discussions around export controls, compliance laws, and competition regulations. Such dependencies reveal both opportunities and economic risks tied to the evolving tensions between the PRC and the U.S., which could potentially disrupt semiconductor manufacturing and supply chains.

The PRC is frequently cited in matters related to operational frameworks, legal actions, and governmental policies that shape the competitive environment within the technology industry. This jurisdiction is critical for compliance with laws regarding competition and distribution, highlighting the necessity for businesses operating in or with the PRC to adeptly navigate its regulatory landscape and the associated geopolitical tensions. Additionally, the market concentration within the PRC poses economic and political risks that are exacerbated by ongoing U.S.-China relations, further complicating the dynamics for foreign businesses and stakeholders engaging in this formidable regional market.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5068f4b1da4cd023617e872a463eeb62&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d028a96cd827e54a97bfc99b9a77942a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-050055b3bc468fa0d183c4f69822f018&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5749c9de1780a43222605dcccf7b84ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3de34ec76f3a0a44857b72c2f6e55416&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-789e78a4c56dfc29b3f11f7927499d10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-588c85ac2130c08f6763faa2a55cecd4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-520988de7bd26059b457c267986b647d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2674cda5d2c8571334c7ce0cb7e9fb3f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6aeca2a51a3e2732d9a306c9c0622909</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1777380550</data>
