  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">East Asia is a region that includes countries like China, Japan, and South Korea, significant for global manufacturing and technology.&lt;SEP&gt;East Asia is a region where chip manufacturing operations are concentrated, making the industry susceptible to adverse developments in the area.&lt;SEP&gt;East Asia is a region where chip manufacturing operations are concentrated, making the industry susceptible to adverse developments in the area.</data>
