<node id="Arm China">
  <data key="d0">Arm China</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Arm China, also known as Arm Technology (China) Co. Limited, is a prominent entity within the semiconductor industry that plays a pivotal role in facilitating ARM's access to the People's Republic of China (PRC) market. The organization serves as a crucial commercial partner and significant customer for ARM, contributing a considerable portion of ARM's total revenue during the recent fiscal years, specifically for 2023, 2024, and 2025. This financial impact underscores the strategic importance of Arm China's operations for ARM.

As part of its role in the PRC, Arm China has established a licensing framework that enables local semiconductor companies and original equipment manufacturers (OEMs) to utilize ARM's processor technology. This licensing relationship is central to Arm China's operational strategy, allowing the company to engage independently while navigating the complex regulatory landscape of technology in China. Despite its association with ARM, Arm China operates under a degree of independence and has various contractual relationships, including obligations to the IPLA, which involves providing financial information and protecting access to intellectual property (IP) and customer data.

The relationship between Arm China and its parent company, SoftBank Group, has been the subject of scrutiny and may involve potential disputes stemming from the competitive dynamics of the technology sector. While Arm China maintains strong ties to ARM, its independent operational status is critical, allowing it to effectively engage in the PRC market despite challenges related to compliance and political influences.

Overall, Arm China serves as a key bridge for ARM in the Chinese semiconductor landscape, significantly impacting ARM's revenue while addressing the complexities of operating within this unique environment.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5068f4b1da4cd023617e872a463eeb62&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8b7994a7b9c5c9289cc48f3afe48287c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d028a96cd827e54a97bfc99b9a77942a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ca207bb382651453029b45cb72e9feff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3de34ec76f3a0a44857b72c2f6e55416&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f6da69316e8a6a8b2389b44396109382&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12e1f77fe538051f6128dd4bc89f0c38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-483298b8ddab3276baf8040d8034d01b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-588c85ac2130c08f6763faa2a55cecd4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-520988de7bd26059b457c267986b647d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b7719f4025b95e35216526990a93506c</data>
