  <data key="d2">Design Wins occur when a customer decides to include an Arm CPU product or related technology in their chip designs, indicating a success measure for Arm.&lt;SEP&gt;Design wins refer to successful selections in competitive bid processes for semiconductor products, critical for securing business opportunities.&lt;SEP&gt;Design wins refer to successful selections in competitive bid processes for semiconductor products, critical for securing business opportunities.</data>
