  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">License and Other Revenue includes revenue from licensing, software development tools, design services, training, support, and other fees not constituting royalty revenue.&lt;SEP&gt;License and Other Revenue is a component of total revenue, primarily driven by new licensing agreements and renewals of existing license arrangements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1bd342ebc79b6c8d6a4c0db7019159b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9fe18d577f076ce03948540ed8563a5c</data>
