  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The IPO refers to the initial public offering of shares, an event that affected the Company's cash flows due to employment taxes payable on vested share-based awards.|&lt;SEP&gt;The IPO refers to the initial public offering of the Company's shares, during which certain fixed monetary amount liability-classified awards were converted to equity-classified awards.&gt;</data>
