</node>
<node id="Income Method">
  <data key="d0">Income Method</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">The Income Method is one of the approaches used to estimate a reporting unit’s fair value in the context of goodwill impairment testing.&gt;</data>
