<node id="Income (Loss) from Equity Investments, Net">
  <data key="d0">Income (Loss) from Equity Investments, Net</data>
  <data key="d1">category</data>
  <data key="d2">Income (loss) from equity investments, net includes changes in fair value of equity method investments, proportionate share of equity method investee income or loss, and gains and losses on marketable and non-marketable securities.</data>
