<node id="Interest Income, Net">
  <data key="d0">Interest Income, Net</data>
  <data key="d1">category</data>
  <data key="d2">Interest income consists of interest received on cash, cash equivalents, short-term investments, and loans receivable, while interest expense relates to finance leases.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8b7994a7b9c5c9289cc48f3afe48287c</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
