<node id="Architecture License Agreements">
  <data key="d0">Architecture License Agreements</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Architecture License Agreements (ALA) allow licensees to develop their own highly customized CPU designs compliant with the Arm instruction set architecture for a fixed fee.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9fe18d577f076ce03948540ed8563a5c</data>
