<node id="Smartphones">
  <data key="d0">Smartphones</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Smartphones are mobile devices that combine the functions of a mobile phone and a computer.&lt;SEP&gt;Smartphones are a key market for the company's products, particularly for royalty revenue.&lt;SEP&gt;Smartphones are consumer electronics that constitute a significant end market for the company's products.&lt;SEP&gt;Smartphones are one of the devices affected by economic conditions and demand, which in turn impacts the demand for products that help create them.&lt;SEP&gt;Smartphones are a key market for the company's products, particularly for royalty revenue.&lt;SEP&gt;Smartphones are consumer electronics that constitute a significant end market for the company's products.&lt;SEP&gt;Smartphones are one of the devices affected by economic conditions and demand, which in turn impacts the demand for products that help create them.</data>
