<node id="Data Centers">
  <data key="d0">Data Centers</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Data Centers are facilities that house and manage large amounts of data and server equipment.&lt;SEP&gt;Data Centers are part of the market where the company's products are licensed and used, and where technological changes are rapid.&lt;SEP&gt;Data Centers are facilities used to house, power, and cool the computing resources central to the internet and various IT operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Data Centers are part of the market where the company's products are licensed and used, and where technological changes are rapid.&lt;SEP&gt;Data Centers are facilities used to house, power, and cool the computing resources central to the internet and various IT operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Data Centers are one of the four primary domains interconnected by Arista's network-as-a-service platform.</data>
