  <data key="d2">The U.S. has had recent resurgence and escalation of trade conflicts with the PRC and other major trade partners, causing market disruptions.&lt;SEP&gt;Trade conflicts are disputes between countries over trade policies, which can lead to economic slowdowns and affect businesses.&lt;SEP&gt;Trade conflicts are disputes between countries over trade policies, which can lead to economic slowdowns and affect businesses.</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
