  <data key="d0">Part I Item 1A Risk Factors</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Part I Item 1A “Risk Factors” is a section in the Annual Report on Form 10-K that discusses the risks and uncertainties that could affect KLAC's business.&lt;SEP&gt;Part I Item 1A “Risk Factors” is a section in the report that provides more information on how government actions could impact the company's ability to provide products and services.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4612ab0f41075ef25aa4070b5715ec41&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0f7533f1c0231555ac5ae30f4d37842</data>
