<node id="Semiconductor Process Control">
  <data key="d0">Semiconductor Process Control</data>
  <data key="d1">category</data>
  <data key="d2">Semiconductor Process Control is a segment that includes etching and deposition solutions for advanced packaging and specialty semiconductor markets, showing an increase in revenue due to industry growth and strong demand for products, especially in the inspection portfolio.&lt;SEP&gt;Semiconductor Process Control is a revenue segment that experienced significant growth in revenues during the specified periods.&lt;SEP&gt;Semiconductor Process Control is a segment that includes revenues from products related to semiconductor process control, contributing significantly to the total company revenue.</data>
