<node id="PCB and Component Inspection">
  <data key="d0">PCB and Component Inspection</data>
  <data key="d1">category</data>
  <data key="d2">PCB and Component Inspection is a segment that experienced increased revenue due to packaging products related to AI and a settlement received related to the cancellation of a technology project by a major Display customer.&lt;SEP&gt;PCB and Component Inspection is a category within the financial report, showing revenue figures and percentages for different fiscal years.&lt;SEP&gt;PCB and Component Inspection includes a range of inspection, testing, measurement, and direct imaging for patterning products used by manufacturers of PCBs, FPDs, advanced packaging, microelectromechanical systems (MEMS), and other electronic components.&lt;SEP&gt;The PCB and Component Inspection is a reportable segment within a company that is affected by reorganization and undergoes goodwill impairment tests.&lt;SEP&gt;PCB and Component Inspection is a revenue segment that experienced growth in revenues during the specified periods.&lt;SEP&gt;PCB and Component Inspection is a segment that includes revenues from the inspection of printed circuit boards and components.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4cef59817c38511355f56938f73f6db2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da2b01ab4070bbe76a7dd3d4ffb383d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b7969877a8fd0841863c700fea233da5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5d617bafedeb6760bbc60c5e3993fb7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1329332311e82d0b2cc6f7232bfaa092&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db3fcbe26ec52d22abad5f9f0435fea6</data>
