  <data key="d0">GHG Emissions</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">GHG Emissions stands for Greenhouse Gas Emissions, which are a focus of environmental laws and regulations, including climate change policies.&lt;SEP&gt;GHG Emissions stands for Greenhouse Gas Emissions, which are emissions scoped into three categories (Scope 1, 2, and 3) and are a key focus area for ESG efforts and reduction targets within the company's operations.&lt;SEP&gt;GHG Emissions refers to greenhouse gas emissions, which are part of the sustainability key performance indicators related to the interest rate under the Revolving Credit Facility.</data>
