  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">IT Systems refer to the collective systems, software, hardware, and networks owned and maintained by KLA and third-party providers, which are used to collect, use, transmit, and store data.&lt;SEP&gt;IT systems encompass various complex systems critical to business operations, including cloud-based services and product development.&lt;SEP&gt;IT systems encompass various complex systems critical to business operations, including cloud-based services and product development.</data>
