  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Cybersecurity Risks are the evolving risks that KLA faces, which include threats from state-sponsored organizations, opportunistic hackers, hacktivists, and various attack vectors such as malware and unauthorized intrusions.</data>
