  <data key="d0">Inspection Products</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Inspection products are items sold by the company, and their sales significantly contribute to the company's revenues.&lt;SEP&gt;Inspection Products are a significant source of our revenues, and any delay or reduction in their sales could materially affect our business.</data>
