<node id="Trade Secrets">
  <data key="d0">Trade Secrets</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Trade secrets and other proprietary information that the company attempts to protect through confidentiality agreements and security measures.&lt;SEP&gt;Trade Secrets are confidential business information that provides a competitive edge and must be protected from unauthorized disclosure or misappropriation.&lt;SEP&gt;Trade Secrets are confidential business information that provides a competitive edge and must be protected from unauthorized disclosure or misappropriation.&lt;SEP&gt;Trade secrets consist of confidential business information that provides a competitive edge, crucial for maintaining business integrity.&lt;SEP&gt;Trade secrets are confidential business information that provide a company with a competitive edge and are considered valuable assets that need protection.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c3b4f2c79e964eb1c327adb0e6e96fea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-789e78a4c56dfc29b3f11f7927499d10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f075ac62ff92ae30a48578e40574de9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f0fafb6f504af3f7a6236b07305461d</data>
