<node id="Semiconductors">
  <data key="d0">Semiconductors</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">Semiconductors are materials at the center of investigations into their impact on U.S. national security due to their importance in high-tech industries.&lt;SEP&gt;Semiconductors are a significant focus in trade discussions and regulatory frameworks, especially regarding exports.&lt;SEP&gt;Semiconductors are a significant focus in trade discussions and regulatory frameworks, especially regarding exports.&lt;SEP&gt;Semiconductors are the materials used in electronics to facilitate the flow of current in a circuit, and are subject to purchase commitments by the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Semiconductors are critical components in electronic devices that are subject to export controls and restrictions.</data>
