<node id="Litigation">
  <data key="d0">Litigation</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Litigation is a comprehensive legal process in which an entity, such as Arm, may engage to protect its intellectual property rights and address various legal claims. This process encompasses legal proceedings related to intellectual property rights, securities, and employee disputes that can significantly affect business operations and potentially harm the organization's reputation.

Engaging in litigation usually incurs various costs and may be influenced by developments in technology, which could lead to an increase in disputes or claims. The legal action associated with litigation may also target the entity in the future, highlighting the ongoing nature of risks associated with litigation and its importance in maintaining the entity's operational integrity and strategic interests. Overall, litigation serves as a critical mechanism for safeguarding rights and addressing conflicts that arise within the corporate landscape.&lt;SEP&gt;Litigation involves legal disputes that can affect a business's operations, involving claims related to various legal issues.&lt;SEP&gt;Litigation is a legal event that may materially adversely affect the company if it becomes involved.&lt;SEP&gt;Litigation refers to the legal process of taking disputes to a court, which may be necessary for the company to enforce or defend its intellectual property rights.&lt;SEP&gt;Litigation refers to legal proceedings involving disputes that may affect the operations and financial state of a company.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a09335734e89edd5d8f3e04bd3466cd8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f1d26aff29032e66965549a44d8a5643&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db288d888bd9fbe8abf743c9d16d17a9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe9aa0edeb1f35465d1cc96dcdb61a4d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2674cda5d2c8571334c7ce0cb7e9fb3f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-648a0e92bd5c796b575fad86bf9fd179&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f0fafb6f504af3f7a6236b07305461d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e31bb121b1f8d055ee99592a3cbb3ab5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daa7b8544edadd0f701ab9d8efd26b8e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1777382051</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
