<node id="Samsung">
  <data key="d0">Samsung</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Samsung is a company with broad semiconductor capabilities and a long-term collaboration with Arm, as stated by Young Hyun Jun.&lt;SEP&gt;Samsung is another third-party foundry involved in the manufacturing of semiconductor products for competitors.&lt;SEP&gt;Samsung is a major competitor in the semiconductor foundry market, providing services and products related to semiconductor manufacturing.&lt;SEP&gt;Samsung is another significant third-party foundry capable of producing leading-edge and near-leading-edge nodes for semiconductor products.</data>
