<node id="TSMC">
  <data key="d0">TSMC</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing Company, commonly known as TSMC, is a prominent and influential entity in the semiconductor manufacturing industry. As a leading foundry, TSMC specializes in the fabrication of semiconductor components and provides crucial manufacturing services to a multitude of technology companies globally. Its advanced manufacturing capabilities include the utilization of cutting-edge 3nm process technology, notably for producing the Arm AGI CPU.

TSMC is recognized for its significant market share in wafer production, catering to a diverse range of clients and representing a substantial portion of the overall wafer market. This positions TSMC as a critical supplier of semiconductor wafers, essential for the production of a wide array of electronic devices and technologies.

Operating as a third-party foundry, TSMC serves as a vital manufacturing partner for many firms, including competitors such as Intel. It is involved in the assembly and production of semiconductor components, which are critical for advanced and next-generation products. TSMC's role is particularly significant in the context of Intel's manufacturing strategy as it looks to advance beyond its 18A technology nodes.

In the competitive landscape of semiconductor foundries, TSMC stands out not only for its manufacturing capabilities but also for its strategic importance to numerous clients and partners across the industry.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0fc487cdc1541b708566fbf837bf0441&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb9c473a56337b1bb1aca06b15d0259d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8bbabddff78452a8a933cb1e0ccd794&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-01c84b34cab452ecda64e168d9c9ea38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-401a34b148ef0ff9e9be44cd80f4dd57&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f6b26aa2f7f768941f9a0f229275f9c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f54f1808f1e84fadb148d1b2c20a5860&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8d9c25644243f4d529d06cf43465d4b4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a11dff4d40bd996fd820c540ecd75a40</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1777381712</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
