<node id="Arm Neoverse V3">
  <data key="d0">Arm Neoverse V3</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Arm Neoverse V3 cores are a component of the Arm AGI CPU, delivering leading performance per core, SoC, blade, and rack, with 6GB/s memory bandwidth per core at sub-100ns latency.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2d1f6742e80ed84d267cfe46fa7c9e31</data>
