  <data key="d0">Santosh Janardhan</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Santosh Janardhan is the head of infrastructure at Meta, who stated that Meta worked alongside Arm to develop the Arm AGI CPU to deploy an efficient compute platform that significantly improves data center performance density and supports a multi-generation roadmap for evolving AI systems.</data>
