  <data key="d0">Meta Training and Inference Accelerator</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Meta Training and Inference Accelerator (MTIA) is Meta's own custom silicon that works alongside the Arm AGI CPU, enabling more efficient orchestration in large-scale AI systems.</data>
