  <data key="d0">ASML Holding N.V.</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">ASML Holding N.V. is a leading multinational supplier to the semiconductor industry, providing hardware, software, and services for the mass production of integrated circuits. It is headquartered in Veldhoven, the Netherlands, and is traded on Euronext Amsterdam and NASDAQ under the symbol ASML.&lt;SEP&gt;ASML Holding N.V. is a company that supplies EUV lithography tools critical for semiconductor manufacturing processes.</data>
