<node id="VMware Merger">
  <data key="d0">VMware Merger</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The merger of VMware with Broadcom, funded by the issuance of 2023 Term Loans and cash on hand.&lt;SEP&gt;The VMware Merger refers to the acquisition of VMware, Inc. by Broadcom, which was a significant event in Broadcom's business activities.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;The merger of VMware with Broadcom, funded by the issuance of 2023 Term Loans and cash on hand.&lt;SEP&gt;The VMware Merger refers to the acquisition of VMware, Inc. by Broadcom, which was a significant event in Broadcom's business activities.&gt;</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-cb82fb0b57380bdf7abd3bbcae084048&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5128d467897e9a6a1ea6d801c0966d6e</data>
