<node id="VMware">
  <data key="d0">VMware</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">VMware, Inc. is a technology company that specializes in cloud computing and virtualization software and services. It is particularly recognized for its software solutions in data center virtualization and hybrid-cloud technologies. Recently, VMware has undergone significant changes, notably being acquired by Broadcom. This acquisition has led to alterations in the company’s operational structure, impacting areas such as labor costs and stock-based compensation expenses. Additionally, VMware's cash flows and financing activities have been substantially influenced during the fiscal years 2024 and 2025 as a result of this integration.

Prior to the acquisition by Broadcom, VMware was under the control of Dell, a situation that raised potential tax liabilities affecting its parent company, AVGO. These financial dynamics suggest that VMware's strategic direction may be evolving. Furthermore, the company has sold its End-User Computing (EUC) business to KKR &amp; Co. Inc., indicating a possible pivot towards further acquisition strategies aimed at enhancing business growth.

Overall, VMware's recent transitions underscore a fundamental change in its business operations, aligning with broader trends in the technology sector that prioritize cloud and virtualization services. The consolidation into Broadcom’s operations could signal a more aggressive approach to its market positioning and business strategies moving forward.&lt;SEP&gt;VMware is a company acquired by Broadcom.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-cb82fb0b57380bdf7abd3bbcae084048&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5128d467897e9a6a1ea6d801c0966d6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-99ce04c1c520fc4abd8bec8e5e164c28&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20ff684928510a0aa4726b57cf95bfc6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09305c77610bfec18789bdfc44505242&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bec87d7e720b04a1fe763dab357e1fa8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db288d888bd9fbe8abf743c9d16d17a9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4ffb6ca21b9e1992311d5ea2722c2f55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a592bb47c530d6e0ab16b656b695aa6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c84b525ec6385a6df80b84b52431bb29</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1777382051</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
