  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Acquisition-related intangible assets are recognized in connection with acquisitions and are amortized over their estimated useful lives.&lt;SEP&gt;Acquisition-related intangible assets are recognized in connection with acquisitions and are amortized over their estimated useful lives.</data>
