<node id="AI Racks">
  <data key="d0">AI Racks</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">AI Racks are specialized systems designed to house and integrate multiple AI-related processing units, facilitating their operation effectively. These systems serve as physical infrastructures for hosting various AI applications, playing a crucial role in the deployment of artificial intelligence solutions. 

The business strategy surrounding AI racks often involves selling or leasing these systems, which can enhance operating margins in the short term. However, this approach could potentially affect future gross margins, indicating a strategic balancing act for companies involved in this sector. The implementation of AI racks typically necessitates a significant financial investment, underscoring their importance in enabling advanced AI operations. 

Overall, AI racks represent a critical component in the ecosystem of artificial intelligence deployment, combining technological sophistication with strategic business considerations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bec87d7e720b04a1fe763dab357e1fa8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c8bbabddff78452a8a933cb1e0ccd794&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ad447284cb0c00dbd8ce518b117c09af&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b09f9d54d4cb00356f5ae233ac0e55c8</data>
