<node id="Shareholder Governance Agreement">
  <data key="d0">Shareholder Governance Agreement</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Shareholder Governance Agreement is a comprehensive legal document that delineates various rights and obligations for shareholders, with a particular focus on SoftBank Group. This agreement provides essential guidelines influencing the relationship between the ordinary shares and American Depositary Shares (ADSs) holders and the management of the company.

One of the key aspects of the Shareholder Governance Agreement is the detailed provision of rights regarding board nominations. It specifies the privileges afforded to SoftBank Group in the governance structure of the company, allowing it to exert control during board selection processes. This arrangement is crucial for maintaining the strategic direction of the company as it pertains to shareholder involvement.

In addition to governance aspects, the Shareholder Governance Agreement addresses the pre-emptive rights of SoftBank Group, which are critical when it comes to the issuance of new shares. By defining these rights, the agreement ensures that existing shareholders have the opportunity to maintain their proportional ownership when new shares are offered, preventing dilution of their equity.

Furthermore, the agreement also specifies registration rights that relate to the resale of ordinary shares by SoftBank Group and its affiliates. These provisions are significant as they facilitate liquidity for shareholders by allowing them to sell shares under defined conditions.

Overall, the Shareholder Governance Agreement serves as a fundamental framework for regulating shareholder rights within the Corporate Governance landscape, particularly emphasizing the powers and responsibilities of SoftBank Group in various corporate matters.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b2b270960deb5554f0e44f652867f7fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0d1065649bee800c972122f59f7fc8a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12e1f77fe538051f6128dd4bc89f0c38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-66a91d342b5fd2e4bb339a793a46f87d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e16505fda28ee8ca6cb7b4381bcec9b8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b9cf777435ca6135f2543fc921d450ba</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1777380681</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Securities Act">
  <data key="d0">Securities Act</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Securities Act regulates the offer and sale of securities in the U.S. and requires registration for rights and securities distribution.&lt;SEP&gt;The Securities Act governs the registration of securities and related transactions in financial markets, affecting the resale of SoftBank Group's Registrable Securities.&lt;SEP&gt;The Securities Act regulates the offer and sale of securities in the U.S. and requires registration for rights and securities distribution.&lt;SEP&gt;The Securities Act governs the registration of securities and related transactions in financial markets, affecting the resale of SoftBank Group's Registrable Securities.</data>
