<node id="Ordinary Shares">
  <data key="d0">Ordinary Shares</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Ordinary Shares represent the common equity held by shareholders in a company, fundamentally embodying ownership rights and entitling shareholders to voting rights and dividends. These shares are crucial to a company's equity structure, allowing shareholders to participate in corporate governance and decision-making processes. Under English law, Ordinary Shares are governed by specific regulations that outline shareholder rights and corporate governance limitations, particularly in scenarios where control is exercised by significant shareholders, such as entities like SoftBank Group.

Ordinary Shares carry vital rights, including registration and resale capabilities based on shareholder agreements, thereby facilitating ownership transfer for shareholders. However, their relationship to American Depositary Shares (ADS) presents complications. While ADS holders do possess certain rights, they do not enjoy full control over the Ordinary Shares unless certain conditions are met. This creates a layer of complexity and risk concerning dividend entitlements and ownership rights associated with Ordinary Shares.

In summary, Ordinary Shares are the foundational equity interest in a company, delineating the rights and responsibilities of shareholders, while also navigating the regulatory landscape defined by local laws. They foster vital participation in corporate affairs, although ADSs introduce additional obligations and potential limitations for their holders.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b2b270960deb5554f0e44f652867f7fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-433cb292a4d13d00542cbbad21ff7c8f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3dfe1f74fc726e8b426f2b5d8c1cf952&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea00358d47980b031f36bff739496ce1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0d1065649bee800c972122f59f7fc8a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0c9786a466ef538bc75df1c91bc31589&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-caf1bb802539f8961349a60bf6c9b66c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7a6b22211eb6bb771a84281effb4664c</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1777380656</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
