<node id="Data Protection">
  <data key="d0">Data Protection</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Data Protection involves safeguarding data from unauthorized access or disclosure, which could be at risk with new technologies.&lt;SEP&gt;Data Protection refers to the laws and regulations concerning the handling of personal data and privacy rights.&lt;SEP&gt;Data Protection involves safeguarding data from unauthorized access or disclosure, which could be at risk with new technologies.&lt;SEP&gt;Data Protection refers to the laws and regulations concerning the handling of personal data and privacy rights.&lt;SEP&gt;Data Protection involves safeguarding data from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure, a significant aspect of networking solutions.&lt;SEP&gt;Data Protection refers to the laws and regulations concerning the handling and security of data in the Company's international operations.</data>
