  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Demand is a key factor influencing ARM's business, dependent on trends in the semiconductor and electronics industries.&lt;SEP&gt;Demand is a key factor influencing ARM's business, dependent on trends in the semiconductor and electronics industries.</data>
