<node id="Altera">
  <data key="d0">Altera</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Altera was a wholly owned subsidiary of Intel Corporation until it was deconsolidated following the sale of 51% of its stock.&lt;SEP&gt;Altera is a former wholly owned subsidiary of Intel Corporation that was deconsolidated after the sale of 51% of its common stock.&lt;SEP&gt;Altera is a company that was sold for 51% of its common stock, resulting in employee exclusions from Intel’s total count.&lt;SEP&gt;Altera is a divested business segment from Intel that is noted for its inclusion in prior operations before September 12, 2025.</data>
