  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The Prior Repurchase Program was a $1.2 billion stock repurchase program completed in May 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;The Prior Repurchase Program was an authorization by ANET's board of directors for a $1.0 billion stock repurchase program in October 2021, funded from working capital and expiring in the fourth quarter of 2024.&lt;SEP&gt;The Prior Repurchase Program was a stock repurchase program that allowed for up to $1.2 billion in stock repurchases and was completed in May 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;The Prior Repurchase Program was a stock repurchase program that allowed for up to $1.2 billion in stock repurchases and was completed in May 2025.</data>
