  <data key="d0">New Repurchase Program</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The New Repurchase Program is a $1.5 billion stock repurchase program authorized by the board of directors.&lt;SEP&gt;The New Repurchase Program was an additional $1.2 billion stock repurchase program authorized by ANET's board of directors in May 2024, also to be funded from working capital.&lt;SEP&gt;The New Repurchase Program is a stock repurchase program that allows for repurchases of an additional $1.5 billion and does not obligate the company to acquire any common stock.&lt;SEP&gt;The New Repurchase Program is a stock repurchase program that allows for an additional $1.5 billion in repurchases and is optional and cancellable by the Company.</data>
