<node id="Arista Networks">
  <data key="d0">Arista Networks</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Arista Networks is a company that collaborates with industry leaders, develops network solutions, and has been recognized in Gartner's Magic Quadrant reports. They have also acquired the VeloCloud SD-WAN Portfolio and announced AI agents to streamline network operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Arista Networks is an industry leader in data-driven, client-to-cloud networking for large AI, data center, campus, and routing environments. It delivers platforms that offer availability, agility, automation, analytics, and security.</data>
