  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Ethernet for Scale-Up Networks (ESUN) is an open OCP workstream aimed at open standards-based solutions for scale-up networks, based on Ethernet.&lt;SEP&gt;Ethernet for Scale-Up Networks (ESUN) is an open OCP workstream committed to open standards-based solutions for scale-up, based on Ethernet, and is open to all.</data>
