<node id="Cadence">
  <data key="d0">Cadence</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Cadence is a global market leader in the development of computational and AI-driven software, hardware, and silicon IP products for engineers and scientists.&lt;SEP&gt;Cadence is a subsidiary involved in the sale of products and services related to EDA software and technology.&lt;SEP&gt;Cadence is the organization mentioned in the context of revenue generation through hardware, IP, and software products.&lt;SEP&gt;Cadence is a multinational corporation that is impacted by the OECD's Pillar Two Model Rules regarding taxation.&lt;SEP&gt;Cadence is the acquiring company that intends to purchase Hexagon’s D&amp;E business as outlined in the purchase agreement.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ed2b32ad29a09feed46df0c963169feb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ff8c5ead4252ae2a31532cc82caa936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-71dff42efadaa177f60791628d62844c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3fdce1044a2c44a0e983bbcf60375f53&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-101b5c99777399059ee552bd297fedd2</data>
