<edge source="SoftBank Group" target="Shareholder Governance Agreement">
  <data key="d7">12.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Shareholder Governance Agreement pertaining to SoftBank Group is a legal framework that articulates specific rights, obligations, and influences that SoftBank Group possesses in relation to other shareholders and corporate governance. This agreement is pivotal in shaping various corporate actions and the composition of the company's board of directors.

The Shareholder Governance Agreement grants SoftBank Group certain rights designed to limit the influence of other shareholders on company matters, ensuring that SoftBank can have a significant say in corporate governance. This includes the ability to designate board candidates based on ownership levels, which reflects the importance of their shareholding in determining the leadership and strategic direction of the organization.

Furthermore, this agreement outlines specific rights related to the allotment of shares and options, giving SoftBank Group a measure of control over securities distribution and related shareholder actions. Registration rights included in the agreement affect SoftBank's securities, further solidifying its strategic position in the corporate structure.

Overall, the Shareholder Governance Agreement serves as a crucial document that fortifies SoftBank Group’s influence over governance while specifying its rights and responsibilities in a complex shareholder environment.</data>
  <data key="d9">board representation,contractual rights,corporate governance,governance rights,pre-emptive rights,registration rights,rights,securities resale,shareholder influence</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-b2b270960deb5554f0e44f652867f7fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0d1065649bee800c972122f59f7fc8a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12e1f77fe538051f6128dd4bc89f0c38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-66a91d342b5fd2e4bb339a793a46f87d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e16505fda28ee8ca6cb7b4381bcec9b8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b9cf777435ca6135f2543fc921d450ba</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1777380780</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
